Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Closed Circle."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the language of mysteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the words "closed circle" refer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to some sort of situation where contact with the outside world has been cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, a mountain villa shut in by a blizzard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or an isolated island attacked by a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a luxury liner heading through the big ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:31.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It doesn't matter how many times you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}whether it's in love, deductions, today, or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A chartered luxury liner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A serial case revolving around inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:39.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Detective Conan" is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What a beautiful view!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We sure were lucky! I was worried for a while there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:49.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He forgot what time our return ship left,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so we got to ride on this big one instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:56.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a good thing this ship just happened to stop at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:01.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We would've been stranded out there for three days if it hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:05.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But I wonder what kind of people would reserve a ship like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about my parents who died in an accident last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish they could've seen me all dressed up today...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,All dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Natsue?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:31.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The two of us were married today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:42.97,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoichi's 2nd daughter\NNatsue Hatamoto (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:42.97,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Natsue's Husband\NTakeshi Hatamoto (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We had our ceremony this morning on Hatamoto Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,the same island you were on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But why did you have it on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The majority of the island belongs to the Hatamoto family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We honor generations of our ancestors there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:04:01.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a Hatamoto family tradition to hold wedding ceremonies on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:09.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We reserved this boat for ourselves, so what are strangers doing on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:11.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They appeared to be stranded, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you go over my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:25.18,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Mariko's husband\NKitaro Hatamoto (47)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:25.18,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Head of the Hatamoto family\NGo Hatamoto (72)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You must think pretty highly of yourself if you're making decisions without approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, of course I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:27.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's been in a bad mood since the ceremony today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, after he ate my food...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Uncle Joji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:40.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew he hated Western-style food,\Nbut I had no idea he'd get that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You call this food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:49.24,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Second son of the\NHatamoto family\NJoji Hatamoto (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems my skills still aren't up to par.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It was really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, lady-killer... What's with the flower on your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:58.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Natsue put it there on the way back from the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:01.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's always been my dream since I was a little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:05.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,to give my beloved this flower that only grows on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:10.26,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Kitaro's only son\NIchiro Hatamoto (21)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Too bad it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Like father, like son!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How long are you going to let him to pretend to be an artist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're his father, talk some sense into him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:22.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell him to give up his hopeless dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I need a word with you! Come to my room later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just have patience, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:41.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He isn't long for this world—he'll be gone soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:48.34,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Eldest Hatamoto daughter, Kitaro's wife\NMariko Hatamoto (43)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:48.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And when he is, nearly all of the Hatamoto fortune will be yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:52.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that, Aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Akie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Do you know something I don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.36,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoichi's daughter &\NNatsue's sister\NAkie Hatamoto (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be {\i1}too{\i0} shocked when you hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:07.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It sounds like Grandfather's going to make the announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,when we get back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:17.96,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Akie's husband\NTatsuo Hatamoto (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Does he even know we're up to our necks in debt over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We have 24 hours until the ship arrives in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We simply {\i1}have{\i0} to do something before then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's me, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:39.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:44.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That was an exceptional speech you gave at the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what I would expect of the man whom Natsue chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Scratching your cheeks when you're embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like your father, Isao Zaiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:03.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Falsify your family registry all you want, you still cannot fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've known all this time that you joined the company
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:11.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and got close to Natsue just to avenge your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:20.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Or my life, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Why won't you speak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,These are the main members of the Hatamoto family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:35.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So all of these people went to your wedding, Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! All nine of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,excluding my late parents Shoichi and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:44.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is rather late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. He still hasn't come back from Grandfather's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe they're discussing some under-the-table business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.80,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Dad not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:09.94,Character Card,Comment,0,0,0,,Hatamoto family butler\NKenji Suzuki (64)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:10.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, though I am certain he will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late, Ichiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you make sure to wash your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say! Do you have a boyfriend, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course not, she's still a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll have you know there {\i1}is{\i0} someone I like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he's really smart, good at soccer, dependable, and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} acting so embarrassed about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:47.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And he's an even better detective than my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean your father's a—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My dad's a detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sir? Your seat is ready, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! You're really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was thinking about some things in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alright? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh? What happened to the flower on your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's strange. Where could I have lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone is waiting for you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Whose voice was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The butler Suzuki's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:38.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It came from Dad's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened, Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,- Grandfather!\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nobody's to enter this room until I say it's OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:12.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It would seem that 40 or 50 minutes have passed since Mr. Gozo's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You were the one who found him, Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:23.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where were you 40 to 50 minutes ago, around 8:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:28.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I was getting things ready for dinner at 8:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so I was in the dining room the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:34.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} see Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} working in a hurry around the tables!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:40.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The door to this room was locked when you found the body, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:40.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What ways are there to lock the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It can be locked from the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but you need this key to lock it from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:52.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And this window doesn't open, so it's impossible to sneak into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, this room was impregnable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Impregnable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're saying that my grandfather committed suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If it {\i1}was{\i0} a suicide, then there's something important missing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He died of blood loss after being stabbed in the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:18.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But the knife used to do it is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:21.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure it wasn't a dagger made of ice or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:25.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Mystery novels are full of things that melt away and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.22,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Would someone seriously commit suicide with something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet this is more of his harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:36.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He wanted to torment us by making every Hatamoto here seem suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He hated everyone in the family, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone except Natsue, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't put it past the old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:50.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then it's decided! It was a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And an extremely simple one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:59.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, take a close look at the doorframe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,See the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If the door was closed when he committed suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,none of his blood could have landed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:13.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's more natural to think that he was stabbed while the door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:19.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! Somebody stabbed Mr. Gozo the instant he left the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who locked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you sure you're a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:39.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! It was Mr. Gozo himself who locked the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone stabbed him outside the room and then kept coming for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:48.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so he locked himself inside to escape his attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But then he ran out of strength and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. That would make the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're such a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:03.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! That means everyone had an opportunity to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The murder took place at approximately 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:10.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Ran, Conan, Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and I were at our table since 7:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so none of us could have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:16.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The same can be said for Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was near our table at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, since the killer wasn't in the dining room at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:25.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...it was one of you seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:32.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,When you entered the room, did you notice anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, now that you mention it, I found this flower in front of the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:43.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:49.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the flower I put on Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:56.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you were really late coming to the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Sis, I was just thinking about things in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't try to deny it, Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:10.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I happened to hear you and Father shouting in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to faint
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:20.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,when I heard that you're actually the son of Isao Zaiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's this Isao Zaiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:35.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He committed suicide when Gozo took over his company, Zaiki Industries, 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:40.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,One year later, his wife died of an illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:45.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and their only son was apparently placed in an institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:48.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,To think that that was Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it true, Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:58.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm Takehiko Zaiki, son of Isao Zaiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:03.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,B-But I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:08.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...got close to Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} so you could avenge your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You decided to become a member of the Hatamoto family
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:14.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and wait for the chance to kill Mr. Gozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:18.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And then tonight, you did just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Natsue! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I had you pegged as a pretty staunch fellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but it looks like I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.19,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Joji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:37.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You gotta be an idiot to drop your flower at the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't, I lost my flower somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:43.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are wiped blood stains on the outside carpet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, was that flower really here on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bread crumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bread crumb lying in a pool of blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Mr. Butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:10.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Was there bread during the wedding banquet this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:14.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But of course—it was an extravagant French meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:20.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Joji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} made it all himself.\NHe runs his own French restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Did everyone eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Everyone but the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He loathed Western-style food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:31.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He said that just looking at bread would make him nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:35.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If Joji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s a chef, he has kitchen knives of his own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Naturally. Chefs like him always own their own set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:44.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come now, children shouldn't pry into other people's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Cool off in this storeroom for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't do it! I didn't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you go, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure are lucky, Aunt Mariko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has killed the old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,he'll never make that stupid\Nannouncement about his inheritance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now the Hatamoto Group will belong to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,the husband of his eldest daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And you can draw as much as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,now that your grandfather's dead, Ichiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:27.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And eventually, you too will become the Hatamoto Group's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't really want that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:35.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you ain't thinkin' of monopolizing the guy's inheritance, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry! All you grandchildren will get—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis, could you not talk about money on the night of our father's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:47.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you to talk? You left the family to go be a chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that Father flat out refused you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:56.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,when you asked to borrow money for your restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanted his money too! So be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm extremely sorry to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but the master wrote up a will
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:13.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,just in case something was to happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:19.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I believe it will be read at the main office in the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,—all of his fortune goes to—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Natsue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:26.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And leadership of the Hatamoto Group is to be given to the man
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,that Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:38.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Then what the hell did I marry Akie for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:42.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you only married me to get my dad's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:48.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! Why else would I live with a tight-fisted bitch like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:51.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you to talk?! You're just a worthless musician!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and get a real job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing, just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,About Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I trusted him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I trusted Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:28.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But he only married me so he could kill my grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never trust anyone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:47.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,My gut feeling tells me that he's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the one you chose, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He couldn't possibly be a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear anything strange just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you hear anything, Natsue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, I did hear something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The sound of something falling into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and then a weird thud from the deck below!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The cause of death was most likely brain damage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,caused by a blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:40.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Judging from the wound,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:43.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,the murder weapon was a steel pipe or something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who would do something this terrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:48.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Takeshi's struck again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible. He was locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The door's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:58.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:03.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:57.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT TIME... "THE LUXURY LINER MURDERS (PART 2)" (DIGITAL REMASTER)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:30.22,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the storeroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:34.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We most certainly locked him inside, but he's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:41.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So Takeshi {\i1}was{\i0} the one who killed Father and Tatsuo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:45.26,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The thud that Conan heard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,was probably the sound of the killer hitting Tatsuo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:49.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The splash he heard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:53.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,was either the sound of the murder weapon being thrown overboard, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:57.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...the sound of the killer jumping into the water
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:22:58.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,after running out of places to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:01.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Takeshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:04.04,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,At any rate, there's still a high possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:06.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,that there's a killer aboard this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:09.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's all withdraw to the dining room for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you saying he could be trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.27,0:23:15.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:19.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,His motive for murder was to exact revenge on Gozo Hatamoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:22.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,who drove his father to suicide 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But for all we know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:29.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...he could be trying to kill everyone in the Hatamoto family!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:49.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Sketch book
